Scenario: User answers if they are allergic to an allergen
When the user inputs a character
Given the user enters 'y' or 'n'
Then move to next question

Scenario: User answers if they are allergic to an allergen
When the user inputs a character
Given the user enters a character other than 'y' or 'n'
Then ask same question again

Scenario: Display allergens score
When the user answers all the questions 
Given the user enters 'Y' or 'N' to each question
Then show the user their allergen score